Subject: drm/amd/display: Remove dangling planes on dc commit state
Git-commit: 524bed9a2b9f7d7f9aa5f62547b1faec2f9bab35
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

When disabling pipe splitting, we need to make sure we disable both
planes used.

This should be done for Linux as well.

